      "title": "[正面] At first I got this game just because I liked Ryke...",
      "summary": "At first I got this game just because I liked Ryker's design and the lovecraftian aspect of it. I however, ended up being surprised by the world building and character designs that I wasn't entirely expecting. I was also surprised how good the story is as well and how generous they are compared to other gacha games. My only critique is that I wish they dwelled more into the lovecraftian aspect and that I hope there is more animations with the visuals (the last one is a personal preference, as I would love to see how they depict the scenary and environment more eloquently and cosmically.) Overall, I've been enjoying this game and love the strategic aspect of it and I hope to see more development in the story and characters overall.",
